	(4533, '', 'Wha... what\'s happening?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4534, 'Thank you for saving me!$B$BI\'m a cook and an alchemist from Stormwind.  I was here looking for local herbs and recipes for my uncle Angus when these quilboar captured me.  If you hadn\'t come around, I\'m sure I\'d have ended up in their stew pot!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4535, 'You can cook?  So can I!  Is there a recipe you can teach me?', 'You can cook?  So can I!  Is there a recipe you can teach me?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4536, 'Hm... yes, I do have a recipe you might find useful.  Let me teach you!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4537, 'You\'re an alchemist?  So am I.  Perhaps you can teach me what you know...', 'You\'re an alchemist?  So am I.  Perhaps you can teach me what you know...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
