	(4706, 'You\'ll have to be patient with me, $n. I\'ve got my Spybot inside working on a very delicate matter. I\'ll be with ya in a second.$B$BOh, and do me a favor, try not to let Lescovar see you... we\'re about to ambush him.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4707, 'GOR\'TESH DEAD?!?!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
