	(4717, '', 'You are indeed powerful, $n. Come to me if it is more work that you seek.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4718, 'My eyes never deceive me, $r. I see great power in you - enough power, perhaps, to further our cause. Find me at the top of the tower.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4719, 'Hi there! The name\'s Gregan. What can I do for ya?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4720, 'Buy somethin\', will ya?', 'Buy somethin\', will ya?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4721, 'Can you tell me how I can get a Videre Elixir?', 'Can you tell me how I can get a Videre Elixir?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4722, 'Sure thing, $n. You look like you can be trusted... Trustworthy! I can spot that a mile away...$B$BAnyway, back to what I was sayin\'. Takes one Evoroot plant to make the Videre Elixir. The rest \'a the ingredients are trivial really, but the Evoroot, well, that can be a bit tricky to get.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4723, 'Key... get the key... Gerstahn has... key.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4724, 'Try and make yourself useful, $r. GET ME OUT OF HERE! The High Interrogator has the key.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4725, 'HEY! HEY YOU! $R! Get me out of here!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(4726, '%s groans.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
