	(5430, 'Emperor Thaurissan does not wish to be disturbed! Turn back now or face your doom, weak mortals!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5431, 'Hail to the king, baby!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5432, '', 'Hello there, my name is Petra.  To my right is my kodo, Dadanga.  We\'re with Marshal Expeditions - been so for a few years now, ever since Dadanga was a babe.$B$BIf you have any lit torches or any open sources of flame, I\'d like to ask you to keep them stashed if you could.  Dadanga dislikes smoke.', 0, 0, 0, 3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5433, 'For the love of all that is holy and dear, please tell me that you\'ve come to deliver us from this forsaken land.  Though I\'m with Marshal Expeditions, I would give you the gold teeth from my mouth to climb inside your backpack and leave this place.', '', 0, 0, 0, 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5434, '', 'Oh, hello there!  I\'m Hol\'anyee, the chief scientist and biologist of Marshal Expeditions.  My brother and I, along with our companions, travel Azeroth exploring the wild and untamed majesty.  It is exciting... but, um... I think we got ourselves into a little too much excitement this time!', 0, 0, 0, 3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5435, 'Hello stranger, and welcome to the untamed majesty of Un\'Goro Crater!$B$BMy name is Williden Marshal.  My sister, our companions, and I make up Marshal Expeditions - scientists and explorers of Azeroth\'s wild and great unknown.$B$BWe\'ve hit a bit of a rough patch here, and we\'re looking for some help if you have the time!', '', 0, 0, 0, 3, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5436, '', 'This is where things get interesting.  My plan is to follow the mountail wall, keeping it to our left.  That way, we won\'t get lost in the jungle and we\'ll cut down on the hostiles.  You ready?', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5437, '', 'Here\'s the eastern mountain wall!  I\'m cutting towards the south now; try and keep up.  We\'re not out of the thick of it yet!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5439, '', 'Here\'s the path out of Un\'Goro!  We made it!  All we have to worry about is the Tanaris desert now.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5440, '', 'Here it is -- the Tanaris desert.  Funny how an inhospitable place like this looks better than a lush jungle once you\'ve been trapped in it forever.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5441, 'You have been sentenced to death for crimes against the Dark Iron nation!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5442, 'The Sons of Thaurissan shall watch you perish in the Ring of the Law!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5443, 'Unleash the fury and let it be done!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5444, 'Haha! I bet you thought you were done!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5445, 'But your real punishment lies ahead.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5446, 'Good riddance!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5447, 'Incredible! Amazing! I don\'t even know what this means!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5448, 'Look at these samples! What does it mean? What does it mean? I\'m going to need time, time to look at all this information. And I\'ll need more information. Information I can\'t get... damn! Think, Laris, think!$B$BWhat are you going to do? What?!$B$BThere has to be a solution!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5449, 'There must be someplace on Azeroth that we can find oozes uncorrupted by the Scourge or anything else. But where?!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5450, 'Is there a difference between ooze and slime?', 'Is there a difference between ooze and slime?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5451, 'No, not that I can tell. It seems to be mostly based on region. Some races have labled them slimes, some oozes. It seems to be preference mostly.$B$BEvery time I\'ve encountered ooze, sludge, or slime they have basically been the same creatures. The differences seem to be based on their environment, which is why we need a pure sample.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5452, 'What do you mean by "pure?"', 'What do you mean by "pure?"', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5453, 'A pure sample would be one that\'s uncorrupted by unintentional influences. We need to find the creatures in the most basic, normal environment we can.$B$BThat means somewhere devoid of civilization or the effects of the dominant races of Azeroth. Someplace... untouched.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5454, 'Are there any areas you can think of that would be so untouched?', 'Are there any areas you can think of that would be so untouched?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5455, 'It\'ll definitely not be anywhere in the Eastern Kingdoms, that\'s for sure.$B$BIt\'ll have to be somwhere on Kalimdor, but still far enough away from the Horde and other races. Someplace unaffected by the Sundering--that means no where near the Night elves\' civilization either.$B$BI would guess it\'d be someplace protected also... like a valley, or a crater. I don\'t know. I\'m just guessing now. I\'m sorry I couldn\'t help you more.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5456, 'I bid you welcome, $c. Rare do we have visitors down to these levels of the Apothecarium... unless of course there\'s something someone wants... or needs.$B$B<Chemist Coely laughs.>$B$BHow can I help you today, hmm?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(5457, 'Come to the aid of the Throne!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
