	(5472, 'Why you would want to leave these sunny shores and crystal blue waters I have no idea. It\'s like paradise down here. But don\'t tell my brother Zapetta that, he\'s bitter enough already about getting stuck up there in Tirisfal all day long. This Zeppelin here drops off at Orgrimmar so you shouldn\'t have to worry about having to listen to him whine. But if you are in Tirisfal anytime soon, heed my warning and don\'t get him started.', 'Why you would want to leave these sunny shores and crystal blue waters I have no idea. It\'s like paradise down here. But don\'t tell my brother Zapetta that, he\'s bitter enough already about getting stuck up there in Tirisfal all day long. This Zeppelin here drops off at Orgrimmar so you shouldn\'t have to worry about having to listen to him whine. But if you are in Tirisfal anytime soon, heed my warning and don\'t get him started.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
