	(5484, 'A fellowship of kindred spirits can be a powerful force.  Krumn will help you to achieve this.  You will find him at the Thunder Bluff Civic Information center on the lower rise next to the lifts.', 'A fellowship of kindred spirits can be a powerful force.  Krumn will help you to achieve this.  You will find him at the Thunder Bluff Civic Information center on the lower rise next to the lifts.', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
