	(5486, 'Any friend of the animals is a friend of mine.  The Hunter\'s Hall is what you seek.  It sits atop the Hunter Rise.', 'Any friend of the animals is a friend of mine.  The Hunter\'s Hall is what you seek.  It sits atop the Hunter Rise.', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
