	(5501, 'I believe I noticed a new shipment of mail being delivered not too long ago.  You\'ll find the mailbox just outside the Thunder Bluff Bank on the lower rise.', 'I believe I noticed a new shipment of mail being delivered not too long ago.  You\'ll find the mailbox just outside the Thunder Bluff Bank on the lower rise.', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
