	(7137, 'You must find a way to show that you both are fighting for the same side. Although the Timbermaw may attack you now, if you are diligent, you will find a way.$B$BYou must remember that any attacks on the Timbermaw furbolg directly will greatly hinder your chances of gaining them as an ally.$B$BA good place to start would be the Deadwood furbolg found in many parts of Felwood. These furbolg are the enemy of the Timbermaw tribe, and slaying them would greatly improve your standing with the Timbermaw.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
