	(7214, 'Well met, $c. You may speak to me unless you have direct business with my mistress Magatha.$B$BI deal with most of her tasks for her so she can concentrate on more important matters. Perhaps there are some things we could discuss before you seek audience with her?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
