	(7418, '', 'Soon after, we began to have visions of a creature... A creature with the feathers of an owl, but the will and might of a bear...', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7419, '', 'It was on that day that the wildkin were given to us. Fierce guardians, the goddess assigned the wildkin to protect all of her sacred places.\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7420, 'A thousand more like him exist. Ten thousand. Should one fall, another will rise to take the seat of power.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7421, '%s falls to one knee.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7422, '', 'But now, many years later, the wildkin have grown more feral, and without the guidance of the goddess, they are confused...\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7423, 'Look what they did to my boy.', '', 0, 0, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7424, '', 'Without a purpose, they wander... But many find their way back to the sacred areas that they once were sworn to protect.\n', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7425, '%s holds the limp body of Taelan Fordring and softly sobs.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7426, 'Your death will not have been in vain, Taelan. A new Order is born on this day... an Order which will dedicate itself to extinguishing the evil that plagues this world. An evil that cannot hide behind politics and pleasantries.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7427, '', 'Wildkin are inherently magical; this power was bestowed upon them by the goddess.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7428, '', 'Know that wherever you might find them in the world, they are protecting something of importance, as they were entrusted to do so long ago.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7429, 'Too long have I sat idle, gripped in this haze... this malaise, lamenting what could have been... what should have been.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7430, 'This I promise... This I vow...', '', 0, 0, 0, 15, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7431, '', 'Please, remember what we have shown you...', 0, 0, 0, 30, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7432, '', 'Farewell.\n', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7433, 'Tragic. The elder Fordring lives on... You are too late, old man. Retreat back to your cave, hermit, unless you wish to join your son in the Twisting Nether.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7434, '', 'Thank you for your help, $n. I wish you well in your adventures. ', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7435, '', 'I want to stay here and reflect on what we have seen. Please see Erelas and tell him what we have learned.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7436, 'Then come, hermit!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7437, 'The bear looks at you calmy and patiently, but says nothing.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7438, 'The bear spirit looks upon you with a calm and peaceful gaze.  You hear a voice speak to you as though it was coming from the bear, but the creature makes no indication that it is speaking.$B$B"Greetings, my young friend.  If you have come to me seeking guidance, then perhaps I can help you find what you seek."', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7439, 'What do you represent, spirit?', 'What do you represent, spirit?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7440, 'I represent the strength which bolsters you as a young druid.  I am the strength of the body, and the strength of the heart.  You have already come to know this in your training, and you draw upon this when you take on the aspect of the bear.$B$BContinue to keep the balance in all things, young one, and keep your perspective clear and true.  When you need me... I will be there for you.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7441, 'I represent the strength which bolsters you as a young druid.  You have come to me to learn this strength, young one, and I will teach this to you.  I will teach you all that is the spirit bear, provided you will listen and understand.$B$BIn order to know what it means to draw upon my spirit, you need to understand the importance of the strength of the body, as well as the strength of the heart.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7442, 'I seek to understand the importance of strength of the body.', 'I seek to understand the importance of strength of the body.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7443, 'Strength of the body is the power and swiftness of action.  You must keep yourself fit at all times, both physically and mentally.  The bear\'s girth highlights its strength, as it is a ferocious foe in combat.  The bear\'s girth, however, belies its lithe agility and sharp mind.  These are surprises you will use to your advantage.$B$BYou must rely on the strength of the bear\'s body in order to master the way of the Claw.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7444, 'I seek to understand the importance of strength of the heart.', 'I seek to understand the importance of strength of the heart.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7445, 'Strength of the heart is what gives you the resolve to take action... action that is rooted in intents that are pure and forthright.  To keep the balance is not to be complacent or banal.$B$BYou must show resolve for that which you believe in, and you must be willing to fight for it.  The mother bear shows endless conviction in protecting her young, as does an elder bear protecting his den.  It is this resolve, this strength of heart, which you must come to know if you are to master the way of the Claw.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7446, 'I have heard your words, Great Bear Spirit, and I understand.  I now seek your blessings to fully learn the way of the Claw.', 'I have heard your words, Great Bear Spirit, and I understand.  I now seek your blessings to fully learn the way of the Claw.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7447, 'It remains to be seen if you are ready, young one.  Even the wisest and oldest of druids are never truly ready when their ultimate time of testing comes.$B$BYou have heard my words, and now you must move on.  Heed what I have taught you.  There will be a time when you will have your strength tested.  You must face your foe as the bear would - with strength of body and with strength of heart.  Learn from the fight, young one.  Go... with my blessings.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7448, 'Greetings, $c.  You are welcome in Nighthaven, as well as all of Moonglade.  The Cenarion Circle welcomes all beings who respect the authority and command of nature.$B$BWhile you are here, please be sure to preserve the balance in all things.  Disturbances are not welcome here, and our wardens are trained to cease all hostilities without question.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7449, '', 'Do you require an illusion?$B$BShould your illusion falter in the midst of your quest, return to me and I shall reapply the guise.$B$BShould you fail in your endeavors, do not give up! Return to me. I shall assist you until you have completed your objectives.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7450, 'Strive to keep the balance in all things, $c.  This is where true harmony lies.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7451, 'Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to teach you.$B$BIt never hurts to reaffirm one\'s place within what I like to call the Great Balance.  As preservers of this balance, we must strive to continually keep our minds clear and our hearts strong.  Training helps us in this regard.', '', 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7452, 'I seek training as a druid.', 'I seek training as a druid.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7453, 'The battle is over, and the people of Darrowshire are saved.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7454, 'The battle is over, and the people of Darrowshire are saved.$B$BThey are saved, $n, because of you.  You are truly a hero of Darrowshire.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7455, 'A darkness had fallen over my eyes, but you tore me from my unholy reverie.  You saved me, $n.$B$BAnd now I beg you... to forgive me.', '', 0, 0, 0, 20, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7456, 'Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to train you.$B$BWe are the preservers of the balance, now and forever, as Malfurion lies in the Dreaming.  Never forget this.', '', 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7457, 'Our master Malfurion remains lost in the Dreaming, $c.  His is the light of a beacon that shows the way for us, and we must do everything in our power to preserve that light.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7458, 'The blessings of Cenarius be yours, $c.  Our leader, Arch Druid Staghelm, guides us and all of Teldrassil to a renewed life!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7459, 'Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to train you.$B$BThere are rumors of strife within the Cenarion Circle, but you should pay such loose talk no heed.  Our Arch Druid, Fandral Staghelm, leads us and all of Teldrassil to glory!', 'Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to train you.$B$BThere are rumors of strife within the Cenarion Circle, but you should pay such loose talk no heed.  Our Arch Druid, Fandral Staghelm, leads us and all of Teldrassil to glory!', 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7460, 'Even within cold, stone walls such as the ones that shelter this town, one may find tranquility and peace.  In fact, you may find them everywhere you are... simply look inside yourself for such balance.', 'Even within cold, stone walls such as the ones that shelter this town, one may find tranquility and peace.  In fact, you may find them everywhere you are... simply look inside yourself for such balance.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7461, 'Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to train you.$B$BThere will be a time soon where the call of the Emerald Dream will take hold in you.  You will hibernate for many years and walk amongst the purest of forms.  It is there and then that your ultimate training will take place.', '', 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7462, 'You merely prolong the inevitable, $r. Succumb. She will free your misguided soul.', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7463, '', 'We work to preserve the balance as Cenarius teaches, $c.  His is the light of a beacon that shows the way for us, and we must do everything in our power to preserve that light.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7464, '', 'Welcome, my $g brother : sister;.  If you are here to train, then I would be delighted to train you.$B$BWe are the preservers of the balance, now and forever, as Cenarius has taught us.  Never forget this.', 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7465, '', 'Thanks again, $n! I\'m very pleased with what we found.$B$BGood luck to you!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7466, '', 'I\'m getting ready to travel up the ridge, $n. I could use some help -- would you like to come with me?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7467, '', '%s begins chanting a strange spell...', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7468, 'Are you ready to fetch, boy?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7469, '%s barks in anticipation.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7470, 'Go get it!!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7471, 'Redpath!  Your life ends, here and now!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7472, 'I am unable to train you.', 'I am unable to train you.', 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7473, 'Good boy! Now put it back on the bone pile.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7474, 'I am looking for some bodyguards that would like to protect the Gizelton Caravan. We are stopped on the road east of Kormek\'s Hut, north of Kolkar Centaur Village.', '', 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7475, 'This is Rigger Gizelton asking for assistance escorting my caravan past Mannoroc Coven. I\'m on the road east of Shadowprey village.', '', 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7476, 'I don\'t train your kind $c.', 'I don\'t train your kind $c.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7477, 'We are but darkness and shadows. Eternal. Invisible.', 'We are but darkness and shadows. Eternal. Invisible.', 0, 0, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7478, 'I seek training.', 'I seek training.', 0, 0, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7479, 'Greetings young rogue. What do you seek?', 'Greetings young rogue. What do you seek?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7480, 'I can not train you. You need to talk to your class trainer.', 'I can not train you. You need to talk to your class trainer.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7481, 'Can\'t help ya, $n. I only train rogues.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7482, 'Can\'t help ya, $n. I only train rogues.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7483, '', 'Sorry, but I only train rogues.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7484, 'Ah... a customer! Talk to my greatest invention, the Vendor-Tron 1000. He has all your needs... some of the rarest items you will ever find on the market anywhere in Kalimdor... not to mention that his programming will not allow any bargaining, so the price you see is the price you pay.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7486, 'No doubt you are another inept simpleton sent from the Dark Lady to train under her champion.$B$B<Nathanos sighs.>$B$BI\'ve sent every one of you back to her in pieces, I don\'t see why it will be any different this time.$B$BMine, however, is not to question why, but instead to do as the Dark Lady bids.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7487, 'Let me take a look at what you have to offer.', 'Let me take a look at what you have to offer.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7488, 'This just happens to be your lucky day; I just completed Super-Seller 680\'s maintenance. There are tons of items for sell at great low-low prices. Go ahead and see for yourself... my brother Cork thinks his Vendor-Tron 1000 will out sell my bot.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7489, 'What kin I do for ye, $n?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7490, 'I\'m lookin\' for rogue trainin\'.', 'I\'m lookin\' for rogue trainin\'.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7491, 'Can you train me how to use rogue skills?', 'Can you train me how to use rogue skills?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7492, 'You look like the type I should watch my coin purse around. Something I can help you with?', 'You look like the type I should watch my coin purse around. Something I can help you with?', 0, 0, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7493, 'I don\'t think you want to learn anything I can teach. Might want to find a $c trainer to help you out.', 'I don\'t think you want to learn anything I can teach. Might want to find a $c trainer to help you out.', 0, 0, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7494, 'Come to learn from the master eh?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7495, 'Yes, I have. Teach me.', 'Yes, I have. Teach me.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7496, 'Do I look like a $c to you? Now run along before I feel the need to oil my blade... in your blood.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7497, 'Elune be with you, $c.', '', 0, 0, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7498, 'Greetings, my friend.  May the Dawn keep you well in these troubled times.', '', 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7499, 'Not so fast, $g guy : lady;... I\'ll not be handing out the reigns of a mighty ram steed to someone that\'s not a proven ally of the dwarves of Ironforge.  Once you\'ve been recognized as friendly to Ironforge, I\'ll gladly show you what varieties of rams I have for sale.', 'Not so fast, $g guy : lady;... I\'ll not be handing out the reigns of a mighty ram steed to someone that\'s not a proven ally of the dwarves of Ironforge.  Once you\'ve been recognized as friendly to Ironforge, I\'ll gladly show you what varieties of rams I have for sale.', 0, 0, 0, 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7500, 'My programming will not allow me to lower the cost of any items.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7501, 'I am curious to see what a bucket of bolts has to offer.', 'I am curious to see what a bucket of bolts has to offer.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7503, 'You\'ve not had a steed until you\'ve taken the reigns of a finely bred Barak Tor\'ol mountain ram, my friend.  Please, feel free to inspect these fine companions to any adventurer.  They\'ll serve you well, believe me.', 'You\'ve not had a steed until you\'ve taken the reigns of a finely bred Barak Tor\'ol mountain ram, my friend.  Please, feel free to inspect these fine companions to any adventurer.  They\'ll serve you well, believe me.', 0, 0, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7504, 'I am the latest incarnation of automated vendors... we will rule the world one day... don\'t tell my boss that I am skimming money off his merchandise...', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7505, 'So sorry to leave a customer but we have places to go and people to swindle. We will be back sometime later today. Good-bye!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7506, 'Time for the Gizleton Caravan to head on out! We\'ll be back soon but if you cannot wait, head north to Kormek\'s Hut. We open shop in about an hour.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7507, 'Sorry, but I am not disposed to sell horses to any individual who is not considered to be at least friendly to the Kingdom of Stormwind.  These steeds are the finest you\'ll find anywhere, and we certainly wouldn\'t want them in the hands of our enemies.$B$BNot saying you\'re an enemy, of course... just earn the trust of Stormwind and then we can do business.', 'Sorry, but I am not disposed to sell horses to any individual who is not considered to be at least friendly to the Kingdom of Stormwind.  These steeds are the finest you\'ll find anywhere, and we certainly wouldn\'t want them in the hands of our enemies.$B$BNot saying you\'re an enemy, of course... just earn the trust of Stormwind and then we can do business.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7508, 'Years of quality breeding techniques and plenty of care allow me the privilege of showing you these horses!  Please, take your time as you consider them for your mount.  A horse is a companion for the ages, friend.  Don\'t sell yourself short - get your steed here today!', 'Years of quality breeding techniques and plenty of care allow me the privilege of showing you these horses!  Please, take your time as you consider them for your mount.  A horse is a companion for the ages, friend.  Don\'t sell yourself short - get your steed here today!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7509, 'Let me browse your goods.', 'Let me browse your goods.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7510, 'You are not known to my people.  A kodo is a mighty steed, and it is the product of love and care by my people; such is not given onto strangers.  Until the elders of Thunder Bluff consider you to be a friend, I cannot offer you the sale of a kodo.', 'You are not known to my people.  A kodo is a mighty steed, and it is the product of love and care by my people; such is not given onto strangers.  Until the elders of Thunder Bluff consider you to be a friend, I cannot offer you the sale of a kodo.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7511, 'Before beginning a hunt, it is wise to ask someone what you are looking for before you begin looking for it.', 'Before beginning a hunt, it is wise to ask someone what you are looking for before you begin looking for it.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
INSERT INTO `broadcast_text` (`entry`, `male_text`, `female_text`, `chat_type`, `sound_id`, `language_id`, `emote_id1`, `emote_id2`, `emote_id3`, `emote_delay1`, `emote_delay2`, `emote_delay3`) VALUES
	(7512, 'Kodo beasts, my friend!  Trained from a young age and raised on the Golden Plains of Mulgore, these fine animals will make even finer steeds!  Please, browse my selection, and see for yourself why we taurens have come to rely on these magnificant creatures!', 'Kodo beasts, my friend!  Trained from a young age and raised on the Golden Plains of Mulgore, these fine animals will make even finer steeds!  Please, browse my selection, and see for yourself why we taurens have come to rely on these magnificant creatures!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7513, '', 'Welcome to the Cenarion Circle, $c.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7514, 'I\'d like to train.', 'I\'d like to train.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7515, 'I am here for training.', 'I am here for training.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7516, 'Let me train you in the ways of the hunter.', 'Let me train you in the ways of the hunter.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7517, 'I am in need of training.', 'I am in need of training.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7518, 'I have much knowledge to impress upon you, $c. You must learn to hunt with honor.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7519, 'I have come for training.', 'I have come for training.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7520, '', 'I train hunters in the ways and traditions of our ancestors.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7521, 'I am in need of training.', 'I am in need of training.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7522, 'Tauren have a passion for hunting; it is something that runs deep with our kind.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7523, 'I am a hunter and wish to train.', 'I am a hunter and wish to train.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7524, 'The Royal Apothecary Society has little patience for fools, as do I.  Perhaps the next time you and I speak of my steeds, you will be considered a friend of the Undercity.  Until then...', 'The Royal Apothecary Society has little patience for fools, as do I.  Perhaps the next time you and I speak of my steeds, you will be considered a friend of the Undercity.  Until then...', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7525, 'On behalf of the Royal Apothecary Society, I am pleased to offer you the finest steeds available for the Forsaken.  These beasts have endured trials and tribulations as we all have, and now they too have emerged stronger and more resilient than mere mortal flesh would have had them destined to be!  Please, inspect them for yourself and see.', 'On behalf of the Royal Apothecary Society, I am pleased to offer you the finest steeds available for the Forsaken.  These beasts have endured trials and tribulations as we all have, and now they too have emerged stronger and more resilient than mere mortal flesh would have had them destined to be!  Please, inspect them for yourself and see.', 0, 0, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7526, '', 'Come learn the ways of the hunter. Pride, honor, and tradition.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7527, 'I can teach you the finer points of Ram Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 'I can teach you the finer points of Ram Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7528, 'I\'d like to train.', 'I\'d like to train.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7529, 'I train and guide young hunters in the traditions passed down many generations.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7530, 'I can teach you the finer points of Mechanostrider Piloting, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 'I can teach you the finer points of Mechanostrider Piloting, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7531, 'I can teach you the finer points of Horse Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 'I can teach you the finer points of Horse Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7532, 'I can teach you the finer points of Tiger Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 'I can teach you the finer points of Tiger Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7533, 'I can teach you the finer points of Kodo Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 'I can teach you the finer points of Kodo Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7534, 'I can teach you the finer points of Raptor Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 'I can teach you the finer points of Raptor Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7535, 'I can teach you the finer points of Skeletal Horse Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 'I can teach you the finer points of Skeletal Horse Riding, provided you have enough gold to cover the lesson!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
