	(7672, 'A mere three hundred years ago, a reckless dwarf named Thaurissan summoned the master from his fiery realm. His return to this paltry world devastated the surrounding lands and created this volcanic Core. Mighty Ragnaros has slept under this mountain ever since. \n', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
