	(7678, 'You\'ve already learned everything I can teach you, $n. Talk to the night elf Lilyssia Nightbreeze in the Mage Quarter of Stormwind if you want to continue your studies. I hear she\'s a good teacher.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7679, '', 'Shut inside this little house, I dream of joining the battles that rage outside the city walls. Still, duty compels me to share my knowledge with others who fight in my stead... for now.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7682, 'Ishnu-alah, $gbrother:sister;. Have you any tidings from abroad? My heart yearns for news of Teldrassil.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7683, 'I am honored to share my knowledge with you, $n. See that you use it well.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7684, 'You must choose a more experienced teacher, for you have surpassed my abilities. I advise you to speak with Lilyssia Nightbreeze here: she has much knowledge to offer.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7685, 'NOW FOR YOU, INSECTS! BOLDLY, YOU SOUGHT THE POWER OF RAGNAROS. NOW YOU SHALL SEE IT FIRSTHAND!\n', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7686, '', 'The druids say that it is only a matter of time until nature itself drives the Horde from Kalimdor. Yet corruption continues to spread throughout our lands, even here on Teldrassil.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7687, '', 'Well done! Your understanding of potions is coming along nicely.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7688, '', 'Unfortunately, there is little I can teach someone with your experience, my friend. Seek out the night elf Sylvanna Forestmoon, who resides in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7689, '', 'Elune-adore, my $gbrother:sister;. You are welcome here. Speak, and I will do what I can to aid you.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7690, '', 'Is it not astonishing what one can create from the plants of the forest? Truly, Elune has blessed us with her bounty.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7691, '', 'You are kind to seek me out, but your skills are beyond my own. Have a word with Sylvanna Forestmoon, just over there. She\'s been looking for another student.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7692, 'Did my sweet lass Kali send you down to me? The apple of my eye, she is.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7693, 'I don\'t suppose you\'re here to talk about my lovely Kali. Fine, then. Potions it is. Anyone ever tell ye you\'ve got a one-track mind?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7694, 'Ye\'re beyond my skill to teach, $n. Go pester Tally Berryfizz; she\'s a gnome living in Tinker Town of Ironforge. Oh, and since you\'re headed up anyway, give Kali my love.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7695, 'Don\'t let those big, innocent eyes fool ye. Tally\'s an expert, all right: I learn something new every day. Why d\'you think I\'m here in Tinker Town? Do I look like an engineer to you? Aye, I didn\'t think so.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7696, 'Put your back into it, $glad:lass;. Hard work and determination--that\'s the way! Don\'t let anyone tell you book learnin\' is all ye need.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7697, 'Och, there\'s nothing I can teach ye, $n. Have a word with Tally Berryfizz over there. She can hardly reach the tables, but when she starts brewing a potion, watch out!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7698, 'You got the look of someone wantin\' adventure. Me, I had enough of that by the time we trolls came here. Now I take each day as it comes, an\' I train other folks to handle adventures for me.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7699, 'Ready for another lesson? All right, then. First, relax. You gotta stay loose to stir a potion just right.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7700, 'You got questions, but they be too big for me to answer, $n. You be needin\' to have words with the orc Yelmak in the Drag of Orgrimmar. He\'ll help you out.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7701, 'All the bottles on this table are potions I brewed today. And they say a watched pot never boils. Ha!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7702, 'They called me stupid, but I\'ll show them. I\'m going to watch every pot I have and prove that they can all boil stuff anyway. Yeah, I\'m on a roll! Who\'s stupid now, huh? Huh!?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7703, 'Can\'t help you. You know more about potions than I do. Besides, I have pots to watch. Talk to Yelmak over there. He knows a lot about potions.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7704, 'Bena works like one possessed. Day and night I have seen her bent over these potions, often going without sleep or food. I know our undead allies need help, but I begin to fear she will do herself an injury.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7705, 'I must have broken hundreds of vials when I first began brewing potions. The glass was so fragile in my clumsy hands. I hope you are more cautious than I was.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7706, 'Your capacity for learning has outstripped mine. You will need to talk to Bena Winterhoof over there for further instruction. Please don\'t take too much of her time, though. She needs her rest.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7707, '', 'Nice to see a friendly face. I don\'t get much chitchat from Apothecary Johaan unless he wants something. He\'s been out of the grave too long. Someday I\'ll be like that, I hear. Creepy. Maybe by then I won\'t care.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7708, '', 'Here to learn about potions? I\'ve got plenty to teach you. I might be dead, but I haven\'t lost my brains. Yet.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7709, '', 'I appreciate the company, but let\'s face it: you have more experience with potions than I do. Talk to Doctor Marsh instead if you want training. He\'s a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7710, 'Once, it is true, I was human. What might otherwise be a shortcoming works to our advantage, $n, for I know human weaknesses intimately.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7711, 'Very well. Cut another lump of flesh from one of these specimens. Let us test what you\'ve learned so far, and we can progress from there.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7712, 'Your knowledge of potions has exceeded mine, but you still have much to learn. Go up the stairs to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. He will teach you true sufferi--ahem. He is a Forsaken who will train you further.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7713, 'Stop giving me that look. I may not be an adventurer like you, but that doesn\'t mean I can\'t have a few muscles. All that stirring makes your arms strong.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7714, 'There\'s nothing more I can teach you. I\'ve heard of a night elf who might be able to, though. Her name is Ainethil, and she lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7715, 'I\'m sorry, $n, but I have no time to spend on novices. You want someone closer to your own skill level. Try the night elf Milla Fairancora, in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7716, 'You\'ve put in your time studying the basics. Now it\'s time to up the ante.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7717, 'You want my help? You got it. What do you need?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7718, '', 'Don\'t let the beady eyes and bushy beard fool you. Vosur\'s a talented apprentice and a good friend, even if I do get a crick in my neck when I talk to him.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7719, '', 'Um, you already know everything I could teach you. Maybe it\'s time for you to talk to someone else. Try the night elf Ainethil in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She\'s got some real talent!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7720, '', 'Hey, that\'s actually not so bad. Alrighty, then. How\'d you like to run an errand for me?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7721, '', 'That\'s nice, $n. Go show whatever it is to Vosur over there. He\'ll answer any questions you have.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7722, '', 'Who are you and why are you bothering me? Oh, right--potions student. Right. What can I do for you?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7723, '', 'Ishnu-dal-dieb, $n. Have you come here in search of knowledge?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7724, '', 'Teaching is not a one-sided trade, $n. As I teach you, I learn more myself, and my understanding grows.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7725, '', 'My apologies, $n, but I do not offer instruction to novices. Instead, talk to Milla Fairancora in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus. She can help you make up for lost time.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7726, '', 'You have learned the fundamentals of making potions, but further study requires greater commitment. Prove your dedication by carrying out a task for me.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7727, '', 'Although I am flattered by your confidence in my abilities, teaching you is beyond my skill. You must go to the Craftsmen\'s Terrace in Darnassus, and speak with the night elf Ainethil. She can help you.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7728, '', 'Even slight alterations to a potion\'s ingredients can change it fundamentally. Patience and precision, young one: they will serve you well in all walks of life.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7729, '', 'My skill at creating potions is inferior to yours. You are ready to speak with Ainethil, just over there. She will understand that you are ready for further instruction.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7730, '', 'Your skill is not inconsiderable. Since you appear to have sufficient experience, there is a matter in which I require your aid.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7731, '', 'Ah, to be young again, and to have discovered potions for the first time. Thank you for refreshing my memory, $n. Now go share that youthful enthusiasm with Milla Fairancora over there.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7732, '', 'I have learned much of potions over the long years, $n, and that knowledge is at your disposal. You have only to ask.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7733, 'I\'m busy, $n. Tell Whuut to handle whatever it is. That young pup has been stewing all day long. He spends much more time like that, and he\'s going to hurt something.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7734, 'I\'m honored to meet you, $n, but your skill at potions is greater than my own. Go see Doctor Herbert Halsey, an undead in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He can help you from now on.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7735, 'I\'ve been looking for a little help. Since you\'ve got the skill, I guess you\'ll do, provided you\'ve also got the guts.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7736, 'You\'re talking to the wrong orc. I don\'t train novices. Talk to young Whuut over there... and use small words.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7737, 'Another student, eh? All right. I\'ll see what I can do to help you out.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7738, 'Glyx and I have an understanding: he keeps me supplied, and I keep him rich. Seriously! What that pirate charges me for a measly pouch of crumpled kingsblood... it\'s enough to make a grown goblin cry.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7739, 'I\'ve got plenty of great recipes for you to take a look at, and at discounted prices, too!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7740, 'What is this? You trying to ruin my reputation? I don\'t teach novices, $gbuddy:lady;. Try talking to the orc Whuut in the Drag of Orgrimmar. He\'s a lot closer to your level of skill. And brains.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7741, 'Herbs are so pricey! I could always use a little something extra, if you know what I mean. Help a goblin out?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7742, 'You\'re better at this gig than I am! You want someone with even more experience than I\'ve got. That\'d be Ainethil, a night elf lady who lives in the Craftsmen\'s Terrace of Darnassus.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7743, '', 'When I first saw the undead, I wept, for I could not imagine their horror and loneliness. The Earth Mother spoke to me then; she sang in my blood. And she told me, "Save them."', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7744, '', 'Can you not sense the anguish of the Earth Mother for her lost children, the undead? Speak quickly, $n. Every second costs me dearly. We must help them find their way back to her!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7745, '', 'I cannot in good conscience spend time training novices while our allies, the undead, are suffering so terribly. Please speak with Kray over there instead; he can help you for now.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7746, '', 'You have some skill, it is true, but every moment I spend teaching you is one more moment the undead will spend in torment. Prove to me that you are worth my time.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7747, '', 'Your potion-making skills are beyond mine. Seek out the undead Doctor Herbert Halsey in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He has the skill to train you further, and you can witness firsthand his people\'s plight.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7748, 'Another interruption. How am I supposed to get any work done like this? Don\'t answer that; do I look as if I care what you have to say? Why don\'t you go bother Mr. High-And-Mighty instead?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7749, 'Me, train you? Come on--we both know I can\'t. It\'s this teaching, you see. My own skills suffer. You want training, go to Doctor Herbert Halsey, a Forsaken in the Apothecarium of the Undercity.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7750, 'If you\'re going to be taking up my time, you\'d better prove you\'re worth it. I ought to get something out of this arrangement, after all.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7751, 'Don\'t waste my time. I have research projects older than you. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben in the Apothecarium of the Undercity. He\'s a Forsaken who can probably manage to teach you the basics.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7752, 'Another student. Wonderful. This is why Lydon belongs to the Royal Society of Snobs and gets to do research, and I\'m stuck being an instructor. If I win another teaching award, I\'ll never live it down!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7753, 'My powers have returned and you have squandered your chance, foolish mortals. Till we meet again.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7754, 'With Algernon to keep me supplied, I can do all my work here without hunting for a single herb. If I never have to see the wonders of nature again, it won\'t be too soon.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7755, 'I have no more knowledge to bestow upon you. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Herbert Halsey. He is a Forsaken who can teach you more advanced techniques.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7756, 'If you seek to become my student, you\'ll need to complete an assignment for me. Prove yourself worthy, and I might even consider rewarding you.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7757, 'I\'m not amused by your audacity in coming to me for training. Go through the archway and down the ramp to the southeast, and talk to Doctor Martin Felben. He is a Forsaken who can teach you the basics.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7758, 'Here to learn? Very well. I suppose you can\'t cause our allies much harm if I teach you. Just as long as you actually do manage to harm our enemies.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7759, '', 'This potion seems to heal less damage every time I brew it, though I use the same ingredients. There can be only one conclusion: the plants are changing. I cannot say why or into what.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7760, '', 'It is time you moved on to a more advanced teacher. In the Feathermoon Stronghold of Feralas dwells the night elf Kylanna Windwhisper. She has a brilliant mind; doubtless she can train you further.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7761, '', 'This is excellent work. Are you ready to undertake a mission on my behalf? I know of no one more qualified.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7762, '', 'Your skill at brewing potions needs to be greater before you can become one of my students. In the meantime, perhaps Sylvanna Forestmoon or Milla Fairancora can help you, just over there.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7763, '', 'Your education is progressing well. You should be proud of your accomplishments.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7764, 'My colleagues and I are gathering the deadliest substances we know and testing their effects on our enemies. Once I have everything I need, I shall brew such plagues as this world has never seen.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7765, 'Incredible. Your potions display a knowledge that rivals my own. I cannot train you further, but talk to the orc Rogvar of Stonard in the Swamp of Sorrows. He\'s known for his cutting-edge experiments.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7766, 'You\'ve got real talent and a passion for making potions. There is one little matter I\'d like you to take care of, though.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7767, 'You don\'t yet have the skill to study with me. Go talk to Doctor Martin Felben over there, or go up the ramp to the southeast and see Doctor Marsh. They are Forsaken who can give you the training you need.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7768, 'Ready for training? Then try to keep up, $n. We\'ve got a lot of ground to cover.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7769, '', 'Once I welcomed darkness, for it was the sister of night. Now it is dark all the time, even during the day, and the forests cry out for sustenance. Unless we act soon, this spreading blight will cover the world.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7770, '', 'Have you come here for instruction in the art of making potions? You were mistaken if you thought that I would offer such a privilege to you, unearned. Go, and do not return to me until you have greater skill.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7771, '', 'Your skill displays an enduring affection for our art, but I would see further evidence of your commitment. I shall charge you with a task. Fulfill it, and I will be content.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7772, '', 'Elune has seen fit to gift me with skill and experience. Now I shall pass them on to you.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7773, 'Kalaran, I have misplaced my torch. I require another.', 'Kalaran, I have misplaced my torch. I require another.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7774, 'Warchief Thrall himself asked me to come out here. I was honored to obey, and it\'s no hardship. I couldn\'t have asked for a better posting than Stonard. Just about any herb I might need grows in the muck here.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7775, 'Don\'t stir the potion like that, you ham-handed farmer! No, don\'t stop stirring it, either! Forget it--just give me that ladle before you start a fire. I\'ll salvage what I can. Now, pay attention.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7776, 'Hmm, well, I can see that you have a little skill at making potions. Whether you\'re worthy to be my student remains to be seen, however. I have a job for you. Impress me.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7777, 'How dare you ask me for training, maggot? What were you hoping for, you slack-jawed yokel, a lecture on the proper uses of silverleaf? Out! You\'re lucky I don\'t thrash you senseless for wasting my time.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7778, '', 'Ah, $gpriest:priestess;, you came along just in time. I appreciate it.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7779, '', 'Argh, the pain. Will it ever leave me?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7780, '', 'Thank you! Thank you, $gpriest:priestess;. Now I can take on those corrupt timberlings with Elune\'s power behind me!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7781, '', 'Farewell to you, and may Elune be with you always.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7782, '', 'Ah, $gpriest:priestess;, you came along just in time. I appreciate it.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7783, '', 'Argh, the pain. Will it ever leave me?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7784, '', 'Thank you! Thank you, $gpriest:priestess;. Now I can take on those humans with your power to back me!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7785, '', 'Farewell to you, and may our ancestors be with you always!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7786, 'Ah, $gpriest:priestess;, you came along just in time. I appreciate it.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7787, 'Argh, the pain. Will it ever leave me?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7788, 'Thank you! Thank you, $gpriest:priestess;. Now I can take on those wendigo with the Light on my side!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7789, 'Farewell to you, and may the Light be with you always.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7790, 'Ah, $gpriest:priestess;, you came along just in time. I appreciate it.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7791, 'Argh, the pain. Will it ever leave me?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7792, 'Thank you! Thank you, $gpriest:priestess;. Now I can take on those gnolls with your power to back me!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7793, 'Farewell to you, and may shadow always protect you!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7794, 'Just a minor adjustment here... ah there we go!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7795, 'I would train ye if I could, but ye need the services of someone a bit more... what\'s the word? Brainy! Look for Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge. Tell \'er Bronk sent ye!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7796, 'Lookin\' to be an engineer, eh? Well, by Muradin, ye\'ve come to the right place!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7797, '%s goes into a killing frenzy!', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7798, '%s becomes enraged!', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7799, 'Where\'s my spinner? I just had it here somewhere...', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7800, 'Your current aptitude exceeds my instructional capabilities. You should enquire further with my fellow Gnome Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7801, 'I would be delighted to aid you in the commencement of your pursuit! Let me grab my spinner and we\'ll get started...', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7802, '', 'I heard the new Henweigh 6000 will be rolling off the assembly line soon. I can barely contain my excitement!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7803, '', 'Well... I hate to admit it, but my sister\'s the one you\'ll have to talk to if you want to continue training. I don\'t know as much as she does... yet! She\'s standing over by the rocket car.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7804, '', 'I\'d love to teach you! Show my sister she\'s not the only one who knows a thing or two about engineering...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7805, '', 'Hello there! My name\'s Jenna! And you? ', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7806, '', 'Oh, you\'ve got oodles of things to learn still. I would teach you everything if I could, but I\'m still learning too! Why don\'t you talk to Trixie Quickswitch in Ironforge, she\'ll help you further your education!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7807, '', 'You want to train? With me? Fantastic! The only thing better than assembling bullets and explosive devices is to share that knowledge with someone else! Let\'s get started!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7808, '', 'Ah, what a beautiful day to blow something up!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(7809, '', 'You need to start learning things that are beyond my expertise! Talk to Lilliam Sparkspindle in front of the tent there. He\'ll set you on the right course!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
