	(8930, 'My scepter... After so many years... You have recovered it! You shall truly be the savior of this place...$B$BPlease listen to me carefully, $n. The head and the rod of the scepter may only be reunited into one at the Stone of Maraudon.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
