	(8987, '', 'Hail, $n!  It is good you came to see me.  We are prepared to launch a ground assuault through the Field of Strife!  Once Warmaster Garrick gets his orders, he and his reavers will cut a swath through the Alliance!$B$BDo you want to deliver those orders, $n?  Garrick is waiting in the Field of Strife...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
