	(8990, '', 'Hail, $c!  Our supply level is high, and we are ready to launch a ground assault through the Field of Strife.  Perhaps if your renown was greater, I would trust you to deliver the assault orders.$B$BSo get out there and fight the Alliance!  Show me you\'re a trusted and capable member of the Horde!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
