	(9518, 'The blade itself had to be crafted in ceremony with the children of the Aspects. A rare occurrence indeed... For not only would a dragon have to willingly heat and mold the enchanted metal with their breath, they would also need to contain the fury of their own enchantment by using their blood as temper.\n', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
