	(9534, 'Have you ever heard of a place called Dire Maul?', 'Have you ever heard of a place called Dire Maul?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9535, 'Aye, but I know it by its true name - Eldre\'Thalas.  It was a bastion of magical power for the night elves many, many years ago.$B$BYou know of Eldre\'Thalas, young one?  One might say that is coincidental to my current plight... but I am one not to believe in coincidence.', '', 0, 0, 0, 273, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9536, 'Why do you say that this is a coincidence, Rabine?', 'Why do you say that this is a coincidence, Rabine?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9537, 'Agents of the Cenarion Circle have uncovered disturbing information pertaining to the current situation in Eldre\'Thalas.  I am at an impasse as to what to do about it, and I will no doubt soon seek the aid of able bodied beings capable of handling themselves in a fight.$B$BTo properly take action in Eldre\'Thalas, however, is to understand the lore of an object known as the Fruit of Fertility.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9538, 'The Fruit of Fertility?', 'The Fruit of Fertility?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9539, 'In ages past, Eldre\'Thalas was a nexus of magical power, and those who dwelt within its hallowed halls wielded immense power.  One such night elf was Millicent Serene - a naturalist who willed the power of nature itself into potent artifacts she forged.$B$BThe Fruit of Fertility was her crowning achievement... she used a specially prepared moonwell to grow an exotic and vibrant vine that was imbued with an aura of protection and growth.  All of Eldre\'Thalas flourished from its existence.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9540, 'But something went wrong, didn\'t it?', 'But something went wrong, didn\'t it?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9541, 'Alas, it always seems like it does.  I - as did the rest of the Cenarion Circle - had assumed that Milli\'s creation was destroyed during the War of the Ancients.  This, as I have come to learn, is far from correct.$B$BThe Fruit of Fertility survived... though now it is known as the Felvine.  It is being corrupted by the demonic lord of that section of Eldre\'Thalas, Alzzin the Wildshaper.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9542, 'What would happen if the Fruit of Fertility - or the Felvine - was allowed to be fully corrupted?', 'What would happen if the Fruit of Fertility - or the Felvine - was allowed to be fully corrupted?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9543, 'I... cannot begin to imagine, $n.  All I know is that I am not going to allow it to happen.  It will be destroyed - if not for our continued safety from demonic taint, then for the memory of Millicent Serene... Milli...$B$BThis, my friend, this is where I hope you will come in.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9544, 'What would you have me do, Rabine?', 'What would you have me do, Rabine?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9545, 'Speak with me, $n - if you are willing, the Cenarion Circle would eagerly accept your generous offer of aid.  The threat posed by the Felvine of Eldre\'Thalas is indeed dire.', '', 0, 0, 0, 273, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9546, '<Demitrian falls to his knees.>$B$BYou have recovered my Master\'s eternal prison!$B$BOh long have I waited for this day and finally, it is realized.$B$BHe must be released!', '', 0, 0, 0, 16, 20, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9547, 'What must be done?', 'What must be done?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9548, 'I hold the vessel of his rebirth. Should you be prepared to take on this task, you will be required to fortify the vessel and ultimately, break the hold of Ragnaros himself!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9549, 'The Firelord and all who dare stand in my way shall reel from my wrath.', 'The Firelord and all who dare stand in my way shall reel from my wrath.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9550, 'The vessel of rebirth must be fortified with elementium. I know of only one source of the mineral: the elemental planes, at the core of our world.$B$BThere is one, an Earthshaper, who may know more than I about the acquisition of such things. You must find this Earthshaper!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9551, 'Greetings and salutations, hero!  I have the latest news from both continents and points beyond for your consideration.', 'Greetings and salutations, hero!  I have the latest news from both continents and points beyond for your consideration.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9552, 'I shall scour the earth for this Earthshaper. What of the essence?', 'I shall scour the earth for this Earthshaper. What of the essence?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9553, 'The corporeal form of Ragnaros must be destroyed. From the remnants, his essence shall emerge. In this weakened state, Ragnaros\' grip on the prison of Thunderaan is loosed. The essence itself acting as a key...', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9554, 'Give me the vessel, Highlord.', 'Give me the vessel, Highlord.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
