	(9570, 'Well done, servant. For so long I have been held captive within the prison of the Firelord. I am once more free to feast upon the out world! The land shall once more be ravaged by the force of the Wind Seeker!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9571, 'Ah, and the fool who freed me shall be among the first to quell my immense hunger.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
