	(9623, 'Ack! Help! Crazed gnome trying to kill me!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9624, 'Bow in my presence, insect! Surely you can feel the power I hold over you.', '', 0, 0, 0, 5, 15, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9625, 'I am in search of a great and powerful Warlock.', 'I am in search of a great and powerful Warlock.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9626, 'So you have come to Niby to learn the secrets of calling down an infernal servant from the Nether.$B$BSilence! Niby knows all!$B$BNiby is not so quick to part with such knowledge. First, you must assist Niby with a very important task.', '', 0, 0, 0, 6, 1, 273, 0, 0, 0),
	(9627, 'What task?', 'What task?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9628, 'There is a powerful infernal named Kroshius northeast of this camp. It is why Niby is here. Kroshius is a greater infernal - an infernal that has lasted longer than expected. You see, nub, an infernal crashes down into the earth with great intensity to serve its master but this intensity fades fast. Once the blazing flames have died down, the infernal crumbles.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
	(9629, 'This is all very interesting but what is it that you want?', 'This is all very interesting but what is it that you want?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9630, 'Do not interrupt Niby, fool! I shall rend the flesh from your bones and use your skeletal remains as a coat rack. Now where was I? Oh yes, so, Kroshius lasted nearly ten times longer than any ordinary infernal. I am not sure why but I am confident that with enough study, I could find out.$B$BI need you to recover Kroshius\' Infernal Core.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
	(9631, 'How do I do that?', 'How do I do that?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9632, 'If I am to teach you the secrets of summoning an infernal servant, you must destroy Kroshius and bring me the infernal core from his burning remains. This, however, is not as easy as it sounds. Kroshius has all but burned out completely. You must reignite his corpse and raise him from the rubble. To do this, however, you must gather some components from other demonic entities.$B$BMy imp, Impsy, shall set you on your way.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
	(9633, 'Kroshius live? Kroshius crush!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9634, 'Stand back! Stand clear! The infernal will need to be given a wide berth!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9635, 'BOW DOWN TO THE ALMIGHTY! BOW DOWN BEFORE MY INFERNAL DESTRO... chicken?', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9636, '%s rolls on the floor laughing.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9637, 'Niby, you\'re an idiot.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9638, 'Silence, servant! Vengeance will be mine! Death to Stormwind! Death by chicken!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9639, 'A Sulfuron ingot?!??! Impossible! I must have it! I must! I must!$B$B$R, I am authorized to make you a grand deal for that ingot. Perhaps you would be interested to know the secrets of the Hand of Ragnaros? Sulfuras, idiot! The legendary hammer of the Firelord.', '', 0, 0, 0, 5, 5, 6, 0, 0, 0),
	(9640, 'Hrm, I\'m listening. What is this offer?', 'Hrm, I\'m listening. What is this offer?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9641, 'In exchange for one Sulfuron Ingot, I am authorized to grant you one copy of the plans to forge a Sulfuron hammer.$B$BNow an adventurer like yourself is probably thinking to $g himself:herself;, "What would I ever need a hammer like that for when what I already own is far superior?"$B$BWell let me tell you something, $g mister:missy;, there ain\'t nothing more superior than what the Sulfuron hammer can become!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9642, 'You\'ve got my attention.', 'You\'ve got my attention.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9643, 'You see, all you gotta do is forge the Sulfuron hammer and find yourself the Eye of Sulfuras. Combine the Eye of Sulfuras with the Sulfuron hammer and it will become Sulfuras! Now I\'m not going to bog you down with any technical information as to where or how or when you can get an Eye of Sulfuras. I\'m sure you\'ll figure that stuff out. Just sign this here contract so that our agreement is binding and our business will be done.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 25, 0, 0, 0),
	(9644, 'Give me the contract.', 'Give me the contract.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9645, 'PEASANT CROSSES LINE.', 'PEASANT CROSSES LINE.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9646, 'YOU ARE THE WINNER!', 'YOU ARE THE WINNER!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
