	(9846, 'Do you expect me to cower before the mighty legion of $n?$B$BYou are nothing to me. Less than nothing. Had I desired your head, it would have been presented to me on a pike.$B$BYou have made the mistake that all mortals make.$B$B<Lord Victor Nefarius sighs.>$B$BTime does strange things to those that use it as a form of currency.\n', '', 0, 0, 0, 6, 1, 273, 0, 0, 0),
