	(9867, 'NEFARIAN IS SLAIN! People of Orgrimmar, bow down before the might of $n and $g his:her; allies for they have laid a blow against the Black Dragonflight that is sure to stir the Aspects from their malaise! This defeat shall surely be felt by the father of the Black Flight: Deathwing reels in pain and anguish this day!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
