	(9900, 'Hail friend - a moment of your time, if I may...$B$BWe have endured much in our trials and tribulations in establishing Teldrassil.  Were the constant strife of the times not enough, we now find ourselves in a dire shortage of cloth.  If you have the materials to spare, I ask that you please donate them.  You certainly would earn the gratitude of night elves everywhere in helping us out!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
