	(9902, 'I\'ve made no mistakes.', 'I\'ve made no mistakes.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(9903, 'In your rush to glory, you assumed that the pace of the game revolved around your actions. Can you even fathom how preposterous that sounds to a being like me? A being that if so inclined could cause your own insignificant thoughts to crush the peanut sized mass of grey matter floating within your skull.\n', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0),
