	(9979, 'Fishing is just so pleasant, mon. You know? I owe my state of bliss to my mentor, the greatest angler in the whole world - Nat Pagle. Have you heard of him, mon?$B$BIf you be looking for enlightenment, Nat Pagle be the one who gonna show you the way. ', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
