	(10033, 'Greetings my friend, and welcome to the greatest show on Azeroth!$B$BPlease, step right up and take in all we have to offer.  Amaze at the wonders that the Darkmoon Faire has uncovered in this vast and mysterious world!  We have spared no expense in bringing you excitement that children of all ages will delight in!', '', 0, 0, 0, 66, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
	(10034, 'Welcome back to the greatest show on Azeroth, my friend!  It is truly a delight to see you once again.$B$BPlease, step right up and once more take in all we have to offer.  Be sure to check around, as we are always adding new and exciting things to the Darkmoon Faire!  Amaze at wonders old and new that we have uncovered!  We continue to spare no expense in bringing you excitement that children of all ages will delight in!', '', 0, 0, 0, 2, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
	(10035, 'Silas, why is most everything at the fair free?  How do you make a profit?', 'Silas, why is most everything at the fair free?  How do you make a profit?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10036, 'It\'s not always about money, clem!  While we receive generous donations - some extremely substantial - our traveling troupe of performers is fueled creatively by a need to brighten this war-torn world.  Don\'t worry about us, but instead let us worry about how to best entertain you.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(10037, 'Ticket redemption here!  Get your tickets turned into prizes!  Step right up!', '', 0, 0, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
