	(10491, 'To catch Gahz\'ranka, you\'ll need a special Mudskunk lure.  I make \'em myself!$B$BBut you need more than just the lure; you need some mudskunks too... you need to place them in the lure to give it a rank old smell!$B$BWhen you have the mudskunks, throw the lure off Pagle\'s Point in Zul\'Gurub... and then grab a drink and wait... but not too long, because Gahz\'ranka is sure to come a\'stomping!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
