	(11183, '', 'Looks like the last of the goods we\'ve collected are shipping out to Silithus over the next $2113w days. And once that\'s done, someone will have to come along and ring the gong on the Scarab Dais, outside of Ahn\'Qiraj, to open the gates. That\'s when our bandages will come in handy.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
