	(11185, 'All is gathered, $c. All is being transported for final preparation to Silithus and should arrive within a day. All of our combined forces await the $g hero : heroine; that will complete the reunification of the Scepter of the Shifting Sands, ring the gong and begin the Ahn\'Qiraj War.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
