	(11210, 'Our work is done. Now we wait on the Alliance to finish theirs before shipping everything over to Silithus.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11211, 'If someone has put together the magic scepter of the sands then the war with the bugs will be soon. I relish it, $c! The last of our war goods are on their way to Silithus and should be there within a day. Go and bring honor to the Horde!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 15, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11212, 'If someone has put together the magic scepter of the sands then the war with the bugs will be soon. I relish it, $c! The last of our war goods are on their way to Silithus and should be there within $2113w days. Go and bring honor to the Horde!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 15, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11213, 'Ours is the path of glory, $r! The puny Alliance is still trying to scrape together their war supplies, while we have gathered all of ours and stand ready to send them to Silithus.', '', 0, 0, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11214, 'I wonder, heroes, what will you do when I manage to destroy this shard? Will the world be beyond salvation?', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
