	(11220, '', 'And now the war, it be comin\' soon. All that be left is the sendin\' of all these goods and weapons to the Cenarion Hold in Silithus, and that is gonna be done within a day. Then some brave soul is gonna have to be ringin\' the gong near those Ahn\'Qiraj gates to open \'em and start the war.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
