	(11233, '', 'The end draws nigh! Even as we speak our supplies are being shipped to Silithus and should arrive within $2113w days. Once there I am sure that all we be assembled in quick order, and then we\'ll be awaiting the ringing of the gong at the gates to Ahn\'Qiraj to start the war. I look forward to analyzing whether our preparatory efforts will make a difference.', 0, 0, 0, 5, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
