	(11256, 'Looks like there be only one more day left to fish until all this here war materiel is shipped over to the Silithus desert mon. Then they\'s gonna be getting\' it all ready, and someone is gonna have to ring that gong down south of Cenarion Hold there to open them gates and be startin\' the war.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11257, 'Looks like there be only $2113w more days left to fish until all this here war materiel is shipped over to the Silithus desert mon. Then they\'s gonna be getting\' it all ready, and someone is gonna have to ring that gong down south of Cenarion Hold there to open them gates and be startin\' the war.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11258, 'Time to relax, the Alliance be way behind us mon. We all done with our collectin\' here, and the final polishes be goin\' on things as we speak. When they get done over in their Ironforge, then we be thinkin\' \'bout movin\' all this stuff to Silithus. \'Til then, sit tight and maybe do some fishin\'.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11259, 'If you heard that all of the Horde and Alliance collections have been completed, then you heard right, $c. All of the goods for the war that we gathered and prepared are in the process of being sent to Cenarion Hold in Silithus, with less than a day until the last of it arrives there. After that I suppose we\'ll just have to wait and see who assembles that scepter to ring the gong with, which will open the gates to Ahn\'Qiraj and herald the war.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
	(11260, 'If you heard that all of the Horde and Alliance collections have been completed, then you heard right, $c. All of the goods for the war that we gathered and prepared are in the process of being sent to Cenarion Hold in Silithus, with less than $2113w days until the last of it arrives there. After that I suppose we\'ll just have to wait and see who assembles that scepter to ring the gong with, which will open the gates to Ahn\'Qiraj and herald the war.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0),
	(11261, 'All of the Horde\'s war effort tasks are completed, young $c. Now we need but wait for the Alliance to also finish theirs and all will be ready for the Ahn\'Qiraj War. Except perhaps for the gathering and reunification of the pieces to the Scepter of the Shifting Sands?', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11262, 'That\'s right, um, $g lad : lass;, all of the war materiel is being transported to Silithus and the last of it should get there within a day. After that, we\'ll all just have to wait and see who puts forth a $g hero : heroine; to reconstitute the Scepter of the Shifting Sands and ring the gong on the Scarab Dais. Only when that occurs will the war begin to open the gates of Ahn\'Qiraj.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11263, 'That\'s right, um, $g lad : lass;, all of the war materiel is being transported to Silithus and the last of it should get there within $2113w days. After that, we\'ll all just have to wait and see who puts forth a $g hero : heroine; to reconstitute the Scepter of the Shifting Sands and ring the gong on the Scarab Dais. Only when that occurs will the war begin to open the gates of Ahn\'Qiraj.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11264, 'While it is true that the Alliance has completed all of their war effort tasks, don\'t let that discourage you, $r. Time is of the essence, but we would much rather that you help in the Horde\'s collections carefully and thoroughly. That seems better to me than making a mistake that could cost someone their life once this war truly begins. Wouldn\'t you agree, $c?', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 6, 0, 0, 0),
	(11265, 'Recover the scepter shard, $n. Nefarius must not be allowed to destr... destroy the shard.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11266, 'I will pull the shard from his sundered corpse.', 'I will pull the shard from his sundered corpse.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11267, 'Looking for this: [Red Scepter Shard]? Come and get it...', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11268, 'Your meddling in demonic affairs ends NOW, mortal!  Face the great corruptor - Xandivious!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11269, 'The Nightmare cannot be stopped!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11270, '%s squeezes the last bit of life out of $n and swallows their soul.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11271, 'Come, $n. See what the Nightmare brings...', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11272, 'A chill is in the air.', 'A chill is in the air.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11273, 'We serve Thrall with great pride.  We\'ll travel as far as is needed to vanquish the enemy.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11274, 'Reporting for duty, sir.', 'Reporting for duty, sir.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11275, 'You\'re just in time, $c.  Do you feel the ground shaking beneath you?$B$BSomething approaches from the hive.  Take a place near the grunts, $n.  I\'m counting on you!', '', 0, 0, 0, 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11276, 'The silithid are no match for the sons and daughters of Orgrimmar.  Soon all that will be left of them are their crushed limbs and wings under our feet, $n.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11277, 'Eranikus, Tyrant of the Dream, has entered our world.', 'Eranikus, Tyrant of the Dream, has entered our world.', 3, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11278, '', 'Very well, $n. I will use the Nightmare object to conjure forth Eranikus.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11279, '', 'Follow me.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11280, '', 'Steel yourselves! Summoning a being this powerful is seldom done with positive results.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11281, '', 'Eranikus is here! Seek shelter! Safety!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11282, 'We will locate the origin of the Nightmare through the fragments you collected, $n. From there we will pull Eranikus through a rift in the Dream. Steel yourself, $c. We are inviting the embodiment of the Nightmare into our world.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11283, 'To Nighthaven! Keep your army close, champion.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11284, 'I will call forth Eranikus when I am given the word.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11285, 'I am ready, Remulos.', 'I am ready, Remulos.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11286, 'The enemy is upon us, stand ready!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11287, 'Merok!  Shai!  To my side!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11288, 'For the Horde!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11289, '%s drinks in the suffering of the fallen.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11290, 'The rift will be opened there, above Lake Elun\'ara. Prepare yourself, $n. Eranikus\'s entry into our world will be wrought with chaos and strife.\n', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11291, 'He will stop at nothing to get to Malfurion\'s physical manifestation. That must not happen... We must keep the beast occupied long enough for Tyrande to arrive.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11292, 'Defend Nighthaven, hero...', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11293, 'Fiend! Face the might of Cenarius!', '', 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11294, 'You are certainly not your father, insect. Should it interest me, I would crush you with but a swipe of my claws. Turn Shan\'do Stormrage over to me and your pitiful life will be spared along with the lives of your people.', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11295, 'Who is the predictable one, beast? Surely you did not think that we would summon you on top of Malfurion? Your redemption comes, Eranikus. You will be cleansed of this madness - this corruption.\n', '', 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11296, '%s lets loose a sinister laugh.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11297, 'My redemption? You are bold, little one. My redemption comes by the will of my god.', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11298, '%s roars furiously.', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11299, 'Rise, servants of the Nightmare! Rise and destroy this world! Let there be no survivors...', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11300, 'Hurry, $n! We must find protective cover!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11301, 'Please, champion, protect our people.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11302, 'We will battle these fiends, together! Nighthaven\'s Defenders are also among us. They will fight to the death if asked. Now, quickly, we must drive these aberrations back to the Nightmare. Destroy them all!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11303, 'It will be done, Eranikus. Be well, ancient one.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11304, 'Where is your savior? How long can you hold out against my attacks? ', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11305, 'Defeated my minions? Then face me, mortals!', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11306, 'Remulos, look how easy they fall before me? You can stop this, fool. Turn the druid over to me and it will all be over...', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11307, 'Let it be known that $n - Horde $C - has earned the undying respect of the Warchief.   $GHe : She; has engaged in great diplomacy with Timbermaw Hold and performed valiant actions for them on our behalf.   $GHe : She; has gone above and beyond the call of duty.  Three cheers for $n - a true hero of the Horde!', '', 6, 0, 0, 5, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11308, 'Let it be known that $n - Alliance $C - has earned the undying respect of Ironforge and the Alliance as a whole.  $GHe : She; has engaged in great diplomacy with Timbermaw Hold and performed valiant actions for them on our behalf.   $GHe : She; has gone above and beyond the call of duty.  Three cheers for $n - a true hero of the Alliance!', '', 6, 0, 0, 5, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11309, '', 'Elune, hear my prayers. Grant us serenity! Watch over our fallen...', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11310, '', 'Seek absolution, Eranikus. All will be forgiven...\n', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11311, '', 'You will be forgiven, Eranikus. Elune will always love you. Break free of the bonds that command you!', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11312, '', 'The grasp of the Old Gods is unmoving. He is consumed by their dark thoughts... I... I cannot... cannot channel much longer... Elune aid me...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11313, 'Eranikus, Tyrant of the Dream, is wholly consumed by the Light of Elune. Tranquility sets in over the Moonglade.', 'Eranikus, Tyrant of the Dream, is wholly consumed by the Light of Elune. Tranquility sets in over the Moonglade.', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11314, 'IT BURNS! THE PAIN... SEARING...', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11315, 'WHY? Why did this happen to ... to me? Where were you Tyrande? Where were you when I fell from the grace of Elune?', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11316, 'I... I feel... I feel the touch of Elune upon my being once more... She smiles upon me... Yes... I...', '', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11317, '', 'Tend to the injuries of the wounded, sisters!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11318, 'It takes a bit of practice to be this close to the silithid and go unnoticed.  I don\'t recommend trying it if you can avoid it.  ', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11319, '', '%s falls to one knee.', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11320, '', 'Praise be to Elune... Eranikus is redeemed.', 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11321, 'Don\'t get me wrong, I\'d rather not be in a tunnel filled with silithid day in and day out, but if hiding here and watching these creatures\' movements is going to help us win the war then I\'ll do it for as long as it takes.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11322, 'Soon we shall rid Azeroth of the silithids\' abominable presence.  Their potential for destruction is much greater than what you\'ve seen firsthand, $n.  Greater, darker powers are behind their activities.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11323, 'For so long, I was lost... The Nightmare\'s corruption had consumed me... And now, you... all of you... you have saved me. Released me from its grasp.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11324, 'But... Malfurion, Cenarius, Ysera... they still fight. They need me. I must return to the Dream at once.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11325, 'I\'m here to retrieve your report.', 'I\'m here to retrieve your report.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11326, 'My lady, I am unworthy of your prayer. Truly, you are an angel of light. Please, assist me in returning to the barrow den so that I may return to the Dream. I, like Malfurion, also have a love awaiting me... I must return to her... to protect her...', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11327, 'And heroes... I hold that which you seek. May it once more see the evil dissolved. Remulos, see to it that our champion receives the shard of the Green Flight.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11328, '', '%s nods.', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11329, 'Let us leave Nighthaven, hero. Seek me out at the grove.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11330, 'The Scepter of the Shifting Sands is whole once more, $n.$B$BIt must be you who uses the scepter. It must be you who heralds in the next age of your people.$B$BWhen you are prepared to ring the Scarab Gong and once more open the gates of Ahn\'Qiraj, I will grant you the Scepter. You have only to ask.\n', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11331, 'I am ready, Anachronos. Please grant me the Scepter of the Shifting Sands.', 'I am ready, Anachronos. Please grant me the Scepter of the Shifting Sands.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11332, 'The Scepter of the Shifting Sands is whole once more, $n.$B$BIt must be you who uses the scepter. It must be you who heralds in the next age of your people. $B$BYou must wait for the armies of the Horde and the Alliance to arrive in Silithus before you may ring the Scarab Gong. The time for war is close at hand.\n', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 15, 0, 0, 0),
	(11333, 'The Scepter of the Shifting Sands is whole once more, $n.$B$BIt is you who must lead your armies into the cursed fortress city of Ahn\'Qiraj and mete justice to its inhabitants.$B$BVenture to Silithus and present the Scepter of the Shifting Sands to Jonathan the Revelator.\n', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11334, 'I\'m ready!', 'I\'m ready!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11335, '', 'This line is mostly filler...', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11336, 'What is an Alliance Commendation Signet?', 'What is an Alliance Commendation Signet?', 0, 0, 0, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11337, '', 'An Alliance Commendation Signet is awarded to a $g hero : heroine; who goes above and beyond the call of duty to the Alliance.  Various Commendation Officers for the factions of the Alliance are located in all of the major cities; speak with the one with whom you\'d like to raise your reputation, and give them the number of signets they ask for!$B$BBy the way, during the war effort here, if you\'d rather receive a material reward for your signets in lieu of reputation, seek out Field Marshal Snowfall.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11338, 'We are united in cause, $r. An ancient evil threatens to extinguish all life on Kalimdor and consume the world with its depravity... Its hatred of all things born of the great Shapers: The eternal Titans.$B$BWe are the first and the last lines of defense against the armies of C\'Thun. If we do not rise up and strike at our enemy, our enemy will surely destroy us.$B$BThe war effort needs you!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11339, 'An Alliance Commendation Signet is awarded to a $g hero : heroine; who goes above and beyond the call of duty to the Alliance.  Various Commendation Officers for the factions of the Alliance are located in all of the major cities; speak with the one with whom you\'d like to raise your reputation, and give them the number of signets they ask for!$B$BBy the way, during the war effort here, if you\'d rather receive a material reward for your signets in lieu of reputation, seek out Field Marshal Snowfall.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11340, 'What is a Horde Commendation Signet?', 'What is a Horde Commendation Signet?', 0, 0, 0, 6, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11341, 'A Horde Commendation Signet is awarded to a $g hero : heroine; who goes above and beyond the call of duty to the Horde.  Various Commendation Officers for the factions of the Horde are located in all of the major cities; speak with the one with whom you\'d like to raise your reputation, and give them the number of signets they ask for!$B$BBy the way, during the war effort here, if you\'d rather receive a material reward for your signets instead of reputation, seek out Warlord Gorchuk.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11342, '', 'A Horde Commendation Signet is awarded to a $g hero : heroine; who goes above and beyond the call of duty to the Horde.  Various Commendation Officers for the factions of the Horde are located in all of the major cities; speak with the one with whom you\'d like to raise your reputation, and give them the number of signets they ask for!$B$BBy the way, during the war effort here, if you\'d rather receive a material reward for your signets instead of reputation, seek out Warlord Gorchuk.', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11343, 'begins to slow!', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11345, 'is freezing up!', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11346, 'begins to crack!', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11347, 'looks ready to shatter!', '', 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11348, 'Anachronos, I have lost the signet ring. Could you supply me with a replacement?', 'Anachronos, I have lost the signet ring. Could you supply me with a replacement?', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11349, 'Around this reindeer\'s neck is a tag with the Smokywood Pastures logo on it and a name - "Metzen".$B$BMetzen looks at you with sad, forlorn eyes.  It is almost as if the reindeer has been immobilized by some unseen force.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11350, 'Sprinkle some of the reindeer dust onto Metzen.', 'Sprinkle some of the reindeer dust onto Metzen.', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11351, 'Metzen\'s eyes light up with reindeer joy as you sprinkle the dust on him.  He shakes his antlers at you and breathes out a heavy sigh of what sounds like relief.$B$BAround you, magical energy begins to swell.  It would seem that something\'s about to happen!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11352, 'Even if you somehow managed to free us without defeating C\'Thun, we would focus all of our powers to see the beast banished back to the hell from whence it came - AT ANY COST.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 25, 0, 0, 0),
	(11353, '', 'Heroes of the Brood? C\'Thun must be banished! We can assist you, mortal!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11354, 'I bear witness to a miracle that stands before me! In one thousand years of captivity, I have not seen a single LIVING specimen - other than those foul Qiraji and silithid - enter these chambers.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11355, 'Soldiers of Kalimdor! Heroes of Silithus! One among you has dealt a vicious blow to our mortal enemies! $n and $g his:her; allies have relieved the Ruins of Ahn\'Qiraj of its merciless leader! Ossirian the Unscarred, scourge of Silithus, has finally been destroyed and his armies wholly dismantled!', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11356, '', 'Look alive, lads!  The enemy has been sighted!  Form ranks immediately!', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11357, 'Be sure to stick around for the next firework show!  Starting at 6PM, they\'re every hour on the hour!', 'Be sure to stick around for the next firework show!  Starting at 6PM, they\'re every hour on the hour!', 0, 0, 0, 5, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11358, 'I don\'t know what they put in those kegs, but it goes down like honey!', 'I don\'t know what they put in those kegs, but it goes down like honey!', 0, 0, 0, 1, 153, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11359, 'After the firework show, they\'ll put out goblets so we can raise a toast!', 'After the firework show, they\'ll put out goblets so we can raise a toast!', 0, 0, 0, 71, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11360, 'Well met, friend!', 'Well met, friend!', 0, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11361, 'Greetings, $c. I am Field Marshal Snowfall, commander of the war effort here. We\'ve a hard road to plow ahead of us, $g lad : lass;, so if you can help out, please do so. And feel free to ask questions.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11362, 'We\'ve done it, $g lad : lass;! The Alliance and the Horde have completed gathering everything that we think we\'ll need for the Ahn\'Qiraj War. Right now the final goods are being taken over to Cenarion Hold in Silithus and the last of it will arrive within a day. After that, some brave $g hero : heroine; is going to need to ring the Scarab Gong with the Scepter of the Shifting Sands to open the gates to Ahn\'Qiraj. When those gates open, the war begins!', '', 0, 0, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11363, 'We\'ve done it, $g lad : lass;! The Alliance and the Horde have completed gathering everything that we think we\'ll need for the Ahn\'Qiraj War. Right now the final goods are being taken over to Cenarion Hold in Silithus and all of it will arrive within $2113w days. After that, some brave $g hero : heroine; is going to need to ring the Scarab Gong with the Scepter of the Shifting Sands to open the gates to Ahn\'Qiraj. When those gates open, the war begins!', '', 0, 0, 0, 4, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11364, 'Have you heard the good news, $c? The Alliance has completed all of its war effort collections! Now we simply await the Horde to finish theirs. When they do, we\'ll begin shipping all of the war materiel over to Silithus, and it shouldn\'t be long after that until the Ahn\'Qiraj War begins.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11365, 'Good question, $c. Last I was informed; we have managed to collect $1997w copper bars out of $1998w needed. Additionally, I am told that we have $2002w iron bars out of $2003w, and $2011w out of $2012w thorium bars requested.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11366, 'Herbs, herbs, hmmm, let me see here. Ah yes, here it is. To date we have accumulated $2047w out of $2048w stranglekelp, $2053w out of $2055w purple lotuses, and $2057w out of $2058w arthas\' tears needed.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11367, 'I received an update on that just a moment ago. It looks like out of $2061w light leather needed, we have $2060w. As for the others, the report indicated that we\'ve gathered $2063w of $2064w medium leather, and $2069w out of our $2071w thick leather quota.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11368, 'Collection of bandages is proceeding according to schedule. As far as linen bandages are concerned, we\'ve gathered $2076w of $2077w. Silk bandages have been tallied at $2082w out of $2083w, and we have $2088w out of $2090w runecloth bandages needed.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11369, 'On the cooked goods front it would appear that we\'ve managed to collect and store away $2092w rainbow fin albacore, out of $2093w requested. Additionally, right now we have in $2098w of $2099w roast raptor and $2101w out of $2103w spotted yellowtail in cold storage.', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11370, 'Throm\'ka, Horde $C, stand proud! I am Warlord Gorchuk, commander of the Horde\'s war effort. There are trying times ahead of us, but we shall prevail, as always.$B$BIf you have questions, you should ask them.', '', 0, 0, 0, 15, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11371, 'The time for war is almost upon us, $c! Both the Horde and the Alliance have finished with their preparations. All of our war materiel is being shipped to Silithus as we speak. I\'d expect the last of it to arrive within a day. When all is assembled there, the one who has completed the arduous task of reassembling the Scepter of the Shifting Sands will bang it against the Scarab Gong and open the gates to Ahn\'Qiraj. Then battle shall be joined as has not been seen in ages!$B$BLok\'tar Ogar!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11372, 'The time for war is almost upon us, $c! Both the Horde and the Alliance have finished with their preparations. All of our war materiel is being shipped to Silithus as we speak. I\'d expect it all to arrive within $2113w days. When all is assembled there, the one who has completed the arduous task of reassembling the Scepter of the Shifting Sands will bang it against the Scarab Gong and open the gates to Ahn\'Qiraj. Then battle shall be joined as has not been seen in ages!$B$BLok\'tar Ogar!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
	(11373, '$C, the Horde has gathered all that it needs for the Ahn\'Qiraj War! Now we wait for the puny Alliance to catch up. When they do, we\'ll begin transporting everything to Silithus. It should not be long after the buildup there is completed that the war will begin!', '', 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
