	(12435, 'The Scourge brought only small forces to bear against each of Azeroth\'s capital cities, while their main forces periodically attack the following lands:$B$BAzshara, the Blasted Lands, the Burning Steppes, the Tanaris Desert, the Eastern Plaguelands and Winterspring.', '', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
